Amakipe azakina 1/4 yamenyekanye

Police FC, Kiyovu Sports, Gicumbi FC, Intare FC, Rayon Sports, Etincelles FC, Gasogi United na AS Kigali ni yo makipe amaze azakina 1/4. Tombora iraba mukanya kuri Stade ya Kigali i Nyamirambo.

17:02

APR FC irasezerewe


APR FC ibifite igikombe cy'Amahoro inshuro icyenda ndetse ikaba iheruka kucyegukana mu 2017, isezerewe itarenze 1/8 nyuma yo kunganya na AS Kigali ubusa ku busa mu mukino wo kwishyura waberaga kuri Stade ya Kigali.

APR FC yari yatsinzwe igitego 1-0 mu mukino ubanza.
